imdb.plot outline: An MTV reality series where people set up their friends on "disaster" blind dates. The victim shows up to their date with an undercover actor/actress who will do their best to turn off/offend/alienate the victim using inside info given by the instigators. If the victim stays for a whole hour, the gag is revealed and they are awarded with $60.
imdb.title: Disaster Date
plot: An MTV reality series where people set up their friends on "disaster" blind dates. The victim shows up to their date with an undercover actor/actress who will do their best to turn off/offend/alienate the victim using inside info given by the instigators. If the victim stays for a whole hour, the gag is revealed and they are awarded with $60.
